headline: Dell nears deal to sell $5 billion in AI servers to xAI, Bloomberg News reports
summary: Shares of the company gained 4% after the report, which said Dell would sell servers containing Nvidia's GB200 semiconductors to the AI startup for delivery this year.  Details are still being discussed and may change, the report added.
